Class LinkedCollection<E>

java.lang.Object
  java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
      datastructures.LinkedCollection<E>
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<E>, java.util.Collection<E>
public class LinkedCollection<E>
extends java.util.AbstractCollection<E>

A minimal implementation of a collection as a singly linked list.The elements are unordered and may contain duplicates. As proposed in Collins book Data Structures and the Java Collections Framework, chapter 7.3.

Version:
(070125)
Author:
Bror Bjerner
